summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing execution of supplemental agreements in connection with Department of the Army "Easements for Right of Way (Pipeline)" Nos. DACW67-2-72-34 and DACW67-2-72-35 granted in connection with those particular projects identified as "Lake Union North, Unit 1, Sewer Separation Project," Contracts No. 1 and 2, respectively.
